		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000001"]
			description: ["Every firearm in the pack is built at the Gun Smith Table, and the table itself is gated behind &eterrasteel&r — Botania's chapter six milestone. The chain runs deeper than vanilla Botania: manasteel here is infused from Soul Land &espirit iron&r, not plain iron, so the road to your first gun passes through cultivation as well as flowers. Terrasteel itself is forged on the Terrestrial Agglomeration Plate from manasteel, a mana pearl, and a mana diamond under a heavy mana payment. If your mana generation cannot fund terrasteel, it cannot fund an armory — build out Botania first."]
			icon: "botania:terrasteel_ingot"
			id: "5C5C000000000002"
			rewards: [
				{
					auto: "enabled"
					command: "/mine_and_slash give xp_times_lvl @p 150"
					elevate_perms: true
