		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000004"]
			description: ["Shotguns — the M870, SPAS-12, and double barrels — share the sidearm's &eHV&r material tier but trade range for overwhelming close-quarters burst. Their recipes lean on HV electric motors, your first machine-grade component in a weapon. In dungeon corridors and boss adds phases, a shotgun deletes whatever reaches melee range without asking your character sheet for permission. Pair one with a longer-ranged primary rather than carrying it alone."]
