		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000005"]
			description: ["Submachine guns and personal defense weapons — the MP5, P90, Vector, UMP45, and Uzi — open the &eEV&r material tier. Titanium is the cost of entry: rutile processed through titanium tetrachloride, reduced with magnesium, and blasted in the EBF. What you buy with it is volume of fire — high rate, controllable recoil, fast handling. SMGs are the workhorse for clearing Mine and Slash map mobs, where a hundred light rounds beat five heavy ones."]
