		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000006"]
			description: ["Assault rifles are the center of the arsenal: the AK-47, M4A1, HK416, SCAR-L, G36K, and their kin. They sit at &eEV&r tier with EV electric motors at the heart of the recipe. An assault rifle does everything acceptably — range, rate of fire, damage per shot — which makes it the default primary from the moment you can afford one until the day you specialize. If you build only one gun production line, build the one that feeds your rifle."]
