		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000007"]
			description: ["Designated marksman and battle rifles — the Mk14, SPR15, SKS, FN FAL, and HK G3 — fire full-power cartridges that hit far harder per round than assault rifle fare. Their recipes step up to &eIV&r tier and tungsten steel: tungsten alloyed with steel at extreme EBF temperatures. A DMR rewards the player who lands headshots at range before the enemy closes — in open-air boss arenas and Atlas maps with dangerous ranged mobs, it is the safest damage you can deal."]
			icon: {
				Count: 1
