		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000009"]
			description: ["Sniper rifles — the AWP, M700, Kar98k, and M95 — are the apex of precision, priced at &eZPM&r tier with naquadah alloy plates and ZPM motors. One aimed shot delivers more damage than any other single trigger pull in the pack. Against Cataclysm bosses with punishing melee-range mechanics, opening the fight from eighty blocks away is not cowardice; it is doctrine. Slow handling and tiny magazines mean a sniper is always paired with a fallback weapon."]
