		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C00000000000A"]
			description: ["Ordnance is the top of the ladder: the RPG-7, the M320 grenade launcher, and the M107 anti-materiel rifle. These recipes demand &eZPM&r field generators — the same components your late-game GT multiblocks are begging for, which is exactly the point. Explosive rounds trade single-target efficiency for area denial and burst damage on grouped elites. Rockets are expensive per shot; treat them as a boss-opener and emergency button, not a primary."]
