		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C00000000000D"]
			description: ["The Ammo Box holds a deep reserve of a chosen caliber and reloads feed from it automatically — iron, gold, and diamond tiers hold progressively more. Two companion mods extend it: &eCurios for Ammo Box&r adds a dedicated belt slot so the box rides outside your inventory, and &eApplied Ammo Box&r links a box to your ME network, pulling replacement rounds straight from AE2 storage. A gunner with a networked ammo box never sees an empty magazine at home base."]
			id: "5C5C00000000000E"
			rewards: [
				{
					auto: "enabled"
