		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C00000000000E"]
			description: ["Hand-crafting rounds stops scaling the day you build an LMG. Industrialize: a GT mixer turning copper and zinc dust into brass, an alloy smelter or EBF line casting ingots, and conveyors or AE2 export buses keeping the Gun Smith Table's supply chest full. Create-side, a depot-and-press line handles plate stock for casings just as well. The target is simple — walk to the table, craft a thousand rounds, walk away. When ammunition stops being a decision, guns become your primary weapon in practice and not just on paper."]
			icon: "gtceu:brass_ingot"
			id: "5C5C00000000000F"
			rewards: [
				{
					auto: "enabled"
					command: "/mine_and_slash give xp_times_lvl @p 150"
