		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000004"]
			description: ["Attachments turn one rifle into five different weapons. Scopes and sights change engagement range, grips tame recoil, suppressors and compensators reshape muzzle behavior, stocks trade handling for stability, and extended magazines buy uptime. Craft them at the Gun Smith Table — attachment recipes stay deliberately cheap so experimenting costs little — then open the gun's attachment screen with the attachment key (see the TACZ controls menu) and slot them in. Re-fit for the fight in front of you: a map-clearing loadout and a boss loadout rarely share a scope."]
			icon: "minecraft:spyglass"
