		}
		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000010"]
			description: ["Guns level up. Every kill made with a weapon feeds experience into that specific gun, and each level raises its damage — the weapon-leveling system rewards commitment to a platform over hoarding a locker of unfired steel. The experience lives on the individual item: a veteran AK that has cleared fifty maps outshoots a factory-fresh copy of itself. Check a gun's tooltip for its current level and progress. When choosing between two similar weapons, the one you have already bled with usually wins."]
			icon: "minecraft:enchanted_book"
