		{
			dependencies: [
				"5C5C00000000000B"
				"5C5C00000000000C"
			]
			description: ["Four arsenals from other wars circulate in Supremacy, and none of them can be crafted — no Gun Smith Table recipe exists for any of them, by design. They enter the world three ways: as drops from the endgame bosses of &eCataclysm&r and &eBosses of Mass Destruction&r, in the loot of high-tier &eMine and Slash Atlas maps&r, and inside the &eArmory Crate&r sold at the Gem Shop. Exact rates are yours to discover. What follows is the catalog of what is out there — so you know what you are looking at when it finally drops."]
