		{
			dependencies: ["5C5C000000000012"]
			description: ["Exotic frames from a Golden Age that never happened here: the Gjallarhorn rocket launcher, the Ace of Spades and Thorn hand cannons, the Hammerhead machine gun, and dozens more. The Destiny arsenal is the largest of the four themed collections, spanning every weapon class from sidearm to heavy. These are boss-tier drops with signature behaviors you will not find on any craftable platform — when one falls from a Cataclysm boss or an Atlas map chest, it is an event."]
